Good Housekeeping - November 2014  UK

284 Pages | True PDF | English | 46 MB 


Good Housekeeping Magazine is one of the most trusted lifestyle publications in the country. For well over a century, it has provided readers with reliable information on finding safe and beneficial consumer products. The magazine's expert advice is supported by the long-standing Good Housekeeping Research Institute, an organization dedicated to testing products ranging from hair and skincare treatments to food and electronics. Each issue offers you tips on improving the quality of everyday life, including topics on relationships and parenting, home decorating, health and dieting, careers, financial wellness, and travel
